description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Disabilities Trust is Hiring in Llanelli!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you an HPC registered physiotherapist looking for an exciting and rewarding role within a brain injury centre? We&#39;re looking for a part time physiotherapist to join our clinical and support worker team at Ty Aberdafen, Llanelli on a 12 month FTC.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Situated in Llanelli, Tŷ Aberdafen offers flexible options of specialist care and support for people with acquired brain injury and complex needs. It forms part of the UK-wide network of services provided by the Brain Injury Rehabilitation Trust (BIRT).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a physiotherapist you will work as part of our team, providing physiotherapy input to service users. You&#39;ll also actively participate in regular clinical supervision to reflect on clinical practice and clinical reasoning. You will manage, support and prioritise a caseload of service users with complex mental and/or physical health needs. In addition to this, you will participate in the planning, development and evaluation of physiotherapy services within a designated team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are we looking for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Suitable applicants will have a degree/diploma within physiotherapy and HPC registered.&lt;br /&gt;- Previous experience within neurology is essential&lt;br /&gt;- Ability to prioritise workload and meet specified deadlines.&lt;br /&gt;- Ability to meet the travelling requirements of the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits will include:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;- A competitive salary of £36,829 (Pro-rata)&lt;br /&gt;- 33 days holiday including bank holidays (Pro rata)&lt;br /&gt;- Life assurance&lt;br /&gt;- Employer pension contribution&lt;br /&gt;- Nationwide staff benefits such as Perkbox and discounted gym membership&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours:&lt;/strong&gt; - 21 Hours&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please Note: This post is subject to a Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) and references&lt;/p&gt;
